      "message": "Convert deadline_exceed to the internal error because:\n\n1. prpc only retries the transient errors. deadline_exceed error is not one of them.(see http://shortn/_Q5ZPKyIKb1) \n2. If a RPC call directly goes to Py BB, it will get the internal error code when timeout. That’s why bb cli retried before the migration. However, a RPC call goes through prpc.Client to Py BB, it gets the deadline exceeded error code.",
